<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV100">
<l>nallār navilkurukūr nakarāṉ tirumāl tiruppēr</l>
<l>vallāraṭik kaṇṇicūṭiya māṟaṉ viṇṇappañ ceyta</l>
<l>collār toṭaiyalin nūṟum vallāraḻuntār piṟappām</l>
<l>pollā varuviṉai māyavaṉ cēṟṟaḷḷaṟ poynnilattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these hundred in a wreath full of words</l>
<l>made in supplication by Māṟaṉ who wears as a chaplet the feet of those who master</l>
<l>the holy names of Tirumāl, the one from the city of Kurukūr, sung by good people,</l>
	<l>will not sink into the false ground</l>
<l>of the Delusive one’s muddy mire of evil difficult deeds that is birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
